    "Therefore, only the person owning the account and concluding the contract with the platform is allowed to receive and use the output.",
    "Consequently, the user might be liable when the account is shared or when the content is transmitted and exploited by third parties, regardless of the purpose.",
    "If the user is held liable for the unlawful content, the provider of the GenAI cannot or if it will, then it will be able to redress against the user.",
    "Similarly, if the user breaches the contract by using the output for a prohibited purpose, then even if the provider would be initially held accountable for the content, it could redress against the user based on the contractual provisions.",
